    • Constructor Detail

      • TeamFoundationServerScm

        @DataBoundConstructor
public TeamFoundationServerScm(String serverUrl,
                                                     String projectPath,
                                                     String workspaceName,
                                                     String userName,
                                                     hudson.util.Secret password)
        Constructor used during serialization (and a few tests). WARNING: do NOT add parameters to this constructor when adding fields for new settings. Instead, add a setter annotated with DataBoundSetter in the "Bean properties" section. See setLocalPath(String) for an example.
        Parameters:
        serverUrl - the URL to the team project collection
        projectPath - the path in TFVC to download from
        workspaceName - the name (or expression) to use when mapping the workspace
        userName - the name of the user account to use to talk to TFS/Team Services
        password - the password or personal access token to use to talk to TFS/Team Services
